---
title: Charred Sweet Soy Hake				 on a bed of fragrant rice
description: Heart-healthy fish means this recipe is lower in calories, but it's also packed with protein and healthy fats. The slightly spicy sweet soy marinade is the standout element in this dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R14_W18_IE_IEQCL13539-3_Main__3high-8797bf05.jpg
